        <PortfolioItem Title="Life For Children Ministry - Social Management System" FileName="">

            <PortfolioBody>
                <p class="mb-2">
                    I built this app for an orphanage in Kenya named Life For Children Ministry (LCM). LCM keeps track
                    of several hundred of Kenya's orphans.
                    Their mission is to find homes for these orphans and connect them to sponsors from around the world.
                </p>
